How to raise money #bitsspark - oyetaxi asks Richa who raised from idg for @zivame
Have a differentiator  have your market well thought out #bitsspark   know why you are picking up money  and team is major
We dintgo through investment banker  we approached investors  did a bit of media held back with investors to get traction first #bitsspark
Participated in forums to get investor attraction  we won super angels with @zivame   but we needed to raise more! Hence investment larger
Get the right vision aligning with your investors. Have your vision clear #bitsspark
Set targets for uptill when you will raise money   six months  if you can't  think hard and take a decision. #bitsspark
Build a business thinking of no investment is available #bitsspark
